h1. Mapping DSL

The mapping DSL allows you customize various aspects of the class mapping, for example:

* Limit the searchable properties using [@only@ and @except@|Searchable Plugin - Mapping - Not All Properties]
* Change a property's mapping by [explicitly declaring its mapping|Searchable Plugin - Mapping - Class Property Mapping]
* Alter a class's mapping by adding [class mapping options|Searchable Plugin - Mapping - Class Mapping]




